CONTRIBUTION POLICY

This project welcomes and encourages contributions. If you find this
plugin useful and make improvements, please consider contributing them
back to the original project via pull requests at:

  https://github.com/imabidin/woocommerce-order-flow-control

While the GPL grants you the right to fork and redistribute, the author
kindly asks that improvements be shared with the community rather than
maintained as separate forks. This helps all users benefit from bug fixes,
new features, and security updates.

All contributions are subject to review and must be compatible with the
GPL-2.0+ license.
